section.para:
Technical support for Anyframe is done through the Anyframe open source community site forum (
http://en.anyframejava.org/forum
), and provides QnA and specific guidelines and solutions for source code. 
When you need technical consulting support for a specific project, 
you can make a request through contact us of the Anyframe open source community site (
http://en.anyframejava.org/about/contactus
). Also, you can request issues on Bug Fix, Improvements, and New Features 
through the issue management system JIRA(
http://dev.anyframejava.org/jira
). For more information, click here (
http://en.anyframejava.org/development/issue

).
